# Archive Directory

This directory stores archived entries from:
- learnings.md (when exceeding 200 lines)
- decision-log.md (when exceeding 100 entries)

Files are archived when they are older than 3-6 months and the main file is approaching its size limit.

Archive naming convention:
- `learnings-YYYY-MM-DD.md` (date of archival)
- `decision-log-YYYY-MM-DD.md` (date of archival)
